{"tid":2076270,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[入面大量五毛] 中國拒參與限武談判 美國貼圖諷中國代表「放飛機」","createTime":"2020-06-23T11:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T12:10:28.000Z","uid":70063,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cb8e49f593be8f29d5824158fe808e67710af9cd","tid":2076270,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:30:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/USArmsControl/status/1274956212723802113?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSArmsControl%2Fstatus%2F1274956212723802113%3Fs%3D19&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=54928404\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSArmsControl%2Fstatus%2F1274956212723802113%3Fs%3D19&h=038eb1df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/USArmsControl/status/1274956212723802113?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n美國與俄羅斯周一在奧地利維也納展開限武談判，中國沒應美國邀請與會，美國代表團在Twitter貼圖宣洩不滿。<br />\n<br />\n美俄《新削減戰略武器條約》（New START）明年2月到期，雙方談判延續或取代《New START》，不過美國一直指中國核力量日增，應參與限武談判，否則美國不大願意延長條約，惟中國一直拒絕成全三方談判。<br />\n<br />\n談判周一舉行期間，美國軍備控制特別代表比林斯利（Marshall Billingslea）在Twitter發文，指中國代表「失場」，「在核力量急增及其他事情上，北京仍躲在神秘長城後」，並配以一張放了中國國旗但沒有中國代表列席的談判桌照片。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部軍控司司長傅聰在比林斯利的推文下以英語留言反擊，說：「奇怪場面啊！未經中國批准就在談判桌展示中國國旗，到底你有多卑劣？」中國駐維也納外交使團也揶揄比林斯利的推文貼圖是「行為藝術」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200623/4WNX27B5DQTCEKVT3UUEC3AHM4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200623%2F4WNX27B5DQTCEKVT3UUEC3AHM4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=fb1e3b23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200623%2F4WNX27B5DQTCEKVT3UUEC3AHM4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=039e0ad4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200623/4WNX27B5DQTCEKVT3UUEC3AHM4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"d5c9f4546c62e5191c63ef23f2a4d9c9240f5edd","tid":2076270,"uid":166785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb8e49f593be8f29d5824158fe808e67710af9cd","tid":2076270,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:30:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/USArmsControl/status/1274956212723802113?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSArmsControl%2Fstatus%2F1274956212723802113%3Fs%3D19&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=54928404\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSArmsControl%2Fstatus%2F1274956212723802113%3Fs%3D19&h=038eb1df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/USArmsControl/status/1274956212723802113?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n美國與俄羅斯周一在奧地利維也納展開限武談判，中國沒應美國邀請與會，美國代表團在Twitter貼圖宣洩不滿。<br />\n<br />\n美俄《新削減戰略武器條約》（New START）明年2月到期，雙方談判延續或取代《New START》，不過美國一直指中國核力量日增，應參與限武談判，否則美國不大願意延長條約，惟中國一直拒絕成全三方談判。<br />\n<br />\n談判周一舉行期間，美國軍備控制特別代表比林斯利（Marshall Billingslea）在Twitter發文，指中國代表「失場」，「在核力量急增及其他事情上，北京仍躲在神秘長城後」，並配以一張放了中國國旗但沒有中國代表列席的談判桌照片。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部軍控司司長傅聰在比林斯利的推文下以英語留言反擊，說：「奇怪場面啊！未經中國批准就在談判桌展示中國國旗，到底你有多卑劣？」中國駐維也納外交使團也揶揄比林斯利的推文貼圖是「行為藝術」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200623/4WNX27B5DQTCEKVT3UUEC3AHM4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200623%2F4WNX27B5DQTCEKVT3UUEC3AHM4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3D